  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Type 2 diabetes, depression, BMI &lt;44,ages between 21-65, female

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  BMI &gt;44, &gt;100 min. of exercise per week, Type 1 diabetes, no diabetes,MI,Stroke,
             Catheterization, unstable angina in previous 6 months,pregnancy,glucocorticosteroid
             therapy in last 3 months,bipolar, psychotic disorder or post-traumatic disorder,moving
             out of area within next 6 weeks
